<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>RESET LOZINKE</title>
    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap');

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      }

      .lijeva {
        flex: 1;
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.45), rgba(0,0,0,0.45)),
          url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1488085061387-422e29b40080?w=1200') center/cover no-repeat;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: flex-end;
        padding: 60px;
      }

      .lijeva h2 {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-size: 48px;
        color: #ffffff;
        line-height: 1.2;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }

      .lijeva p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
        font-weight: 300;
        max-width: 380px;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .desna {
        width: 480px;
        background-color: #fafaf8;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 70px 60px;
      }

      .logo {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-size: 22px;
        color: #1a1a1a;
        margin-bottom: 60px;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

      .logo span {
        color: #c8a96e;
      }

      h1 {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-size: 30px;
        color: #1a1a1a;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .podnaslov {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #999;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        font-weight: 300;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      label {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      input {
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #fff;
        border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        color: #1a1a1a;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 15px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        outline: none;
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        transition: border-color 0.2s;
      }

      input:focus {
        border-color: #c8a96e;
      }

      button {
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #1a1a1a;
        color: #fff;
        border: none;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 15px;
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 500;
        cursor: pointer;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        transition: background-color 0.2s;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      button:hover {
        background-color: #333;
      }

      .divider {
        height: 1px;
        background-color: #e8e8e8;
        margin: 30px 0;
      }

      .login-link {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #999;
      }

      .login-link a {
        color: #1a1a1a;
        font-weight: 500;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .login-link a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <div class="lijeva">
      <h2>Zaboravili ste<br>lozinku?</h2>
      <p>Ne brinite, desava se svima. Unesite vaše podatke i poslat ćemo vam novu lozinku.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="desna">
      <div class="logo">TERRA<span>VISTA</span></div>

      <h1>Reset lozinke</h1>
      <p class="podnaslov">Unesite vaše korisničko ime i email adresu kako bismo vam poslali novu lozinku.</p>

      <form action="/password-reset" method="POST">
        <label>Korisničko ime</label>
        <input type="text" name="ime" placeholder="Unesite vaše ime"/>

        <label>E-mail adresa</label>
        <input type="email" name="mail" placeholder="vas@email.com"/>

        <button type="submit">POŠALJI NOVU LOZINKU</button>
      </form>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div class="login-link">
        Sjetili ste se? <a href="/login">Prijavite se</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>